Class BaseIdentityIndex

  • java.lang.Object
    • sailpoint.tools.xml.AbstractXmlObject

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, sailpoint.tools.xml.PersistentXmlObject, sailpoint.tools.xml.XMLReferenceTarget
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GroupIndex, Scorecard
    public class BaseIdentityIndex
extends GenericIndex
    A class holding various scores and statistics calculated for identities or groups of identities. This is the base class for both GroupIndex and Scorecard.
